sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant SPA as Asset dashboard SPA
  participant API as Authenticated API
  participant DW as DW tables indexes MVs

  Note over SPA: URL params q filters cursor no full catalog in browser
  U->>SPA: search and filters
  SPA->>API: GET /api/assets?q=...&cursor=...
  API->>API: verify JWT session RBAC
  API->>DW: parameterized query LIMIT
  Note over DW: indexes MV slim rows
  DW-->>API: page optional facets
  API-->>SPA: JSON
  SPA-->>U: virtualized list

  U->>SPA: open detail
  SPA->>API: GET /api/assets/:id
  API->>DW: primary-key lookup
  DW-->>API: single row
  API-->>SPA: detail JSON
  SPA-->>U: detail view
